# Duo — environment variables
#
# Copy to `.env` and fill in for local builds. `.env` is gitignored —
# never commit real values. The names are the contract; values live
# only on the build machine (and in 1Password as a backup).
#
# These are only needed when building a signed + notarized DMG
# (Stage 21). For day-to-day `npm run dev` and `npm run dist` with
# `sign: false`, none of these are required.

# === Code-signing (Stage 21) ================================================

# Developer ID Application cert common name as it appears in Keychain Access.
# Format: "Developer ID Application: <Legal Name> (<TEAMID>)"
# Leave unset to let electron-builder auto-pick the only matching cert.
# CSC_NAME=

# === Notarization via App Store Connect API key (Stage 21) =================

# Absolute path to the .p8 key file. Recommended location:
#   ~/.appstoreconnect/private_keys/AuthKey_<KEYID>.p8
# (notarytool also reads this path automatically if placed there.)
# APPLE_API_KEY=

# 10-character Key ID from App Store Connect → Users and Access → Integrations
# APPLE_API_KEY_ID=

# Issuer UUID from App Store Connect → Users and Access → Integrations
# APPLE_API_ISSUER=

# 10-character Team ID from developer.apple.com → Membership
# APPLE_TEAM_ID=
